=== 總督 ===
總督是加納君主的代表，行使了君主的大部分權力<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Vandrei|first=Martha|date=2018-07-19|title=‘That ubiquitous monarch’|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.1093/oso/9780198816720.003.0007|journal=Oxford Scholarship Online|doi=10.1093/oso/9780198816720.003.0007}}</ref>。總督被任命為無限期任職，為君主服務。《[[1931年西敏法令|1931年西敏法令]]》通過後<ref>{{Citation|last=Ibingira|first=Grace Stuart|title=Ghana|date=2019-04-30|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.4324/9780429052002-4|work=African Upheavals Since Independence|pages=51–59|publisher=Routledge|isbn=978-0-429-05200-2|access-date=2020-05-30}}</ref>，總督根據加納內閣的意見，不經英國政府的參與而被任命<ref>{{Citation|title=Lewis, Sir Allen (Montgomery), (26 Oct. 1909–18 Feb. 1993), Governor-General of St Lucia, 1982–87 (first Governor-General, 1979–80; Governor, 1974–79)|date=2007-12-01|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.1093/ww/9780199540884.013.u173811|work=Who Was Who|publisher=Oxford University Press|access-date=2020-05-30}}</ref>。如總督一職出現空缺，終審法院首席法官擔任管理政府官員<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Prempeh|first=H. Kwasi|date=2013-07-30|title=Constitutional autochthony and the invention and survival of “absolute presidentialism” in postcolonial Africa|url=https://www.elgaronline.com/view/edcoll/9781781952108/9781781952108.00020.xml|journal=Order from Transfer|language=en-US}}</ref>。
